claim.claim-text:
7. An image display device for displaying images, comprising: 
a display for displaying the images; 
a storage for storing gradation tables that specify gradation characteristics corresponding to multiple maximum luminance; 
a sensor for measuring the maximum luminance that is output by the display section; and 
a processor for performing gradation correction processing specified by the gradation table on the image displayed on the display section by retrieving from the gradation table storing means the gradation table corresponding to the maximum luminance measured by the luminance measuring means.
